# Realtime Documentation

## Overview
Complete realtime guide. WebSocket connection guide. Subscription examples. Event types. Lifecycle management. Developers can implement realtime features confidently.

## Technical Approach
Comprehensive documentation for realtime service. Explain WebSocket protocol. Show subscription syntax. Document event types. Explain connection lifecycle. Provide working examples.

## User Stories

